      <scopecontent id="aspace_471a33e0b44b3f26cb26e5fc98af217b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of letters, speeches, and planning and logistics records documenting the inauguration of Peter Salovey as Yale's incoming president.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_4830faf1b0227c31f57e0aa3331c17b5">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The records are restricted for a period of thirty-five (35) years following the end of Peter Salovey's tenure as Yale University President.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <odd id="aspace_48b60898895bb82995dd22e0823491e6">
         <head>Note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-A (YRG 2-A), Records of Yale president's office.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_869c003db0a226837d859bef2f1b19da">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the President, 2014-2015.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <prefercite id="aspace_42de5387b07326f40228889a9afc7ee3">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Peter Salovey, President of Yale University, Inauguration Records (RU 1138).  Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <userestrict id="aspace_96e2256fcf24875bd2d8a72eaf531240">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright for materials authored or otherwise produced as official business of Yale University is retained by Yale University. Copyright status for other collection materials is unknown. Transmission or reproduction of materials protected by U.S. Copyright Law (Title 17, U.S.C.) beyond that allowed by fair use requires the written permission of the copyright owners. Works not in the public domain cannot be commercially exploited without permission of the copyright owners. Responsibility for any use rests exclusively with the user.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <relatedmaterial id="aspace_893a00f8b6fb09b801655653a77afeac">
         <head>Related Materials Note</head>
         <p>RU 1129, Office of the Secretary, Yale University, video footage of the inauguration of Peter Salovey (320660 Megabytes).</p>  
      </relatedmaterial>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_742d4f8ff1c0b11c14482f93a824aff9">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
